# Bookstore Test Plan

Objective:
Verify functionality and stability of the online bookstore's core features.

Features to Test:
- User Login
- Book Search
- Add to Cart
- Checkout Process
- Error Handling

Test Types:
- Manual Functional Testing
- Regression Testing
- Smoke Testing
- Exploratory Testing

Entry Criteria:
- Features deployed to test environment

Exit Criteria
- All critical test cases pass
- No open high-severity defects
